data.description: Looking for some space? This beautiful 5-bedroom home, with over 3500 square feet of living space in the sought after subdivision of Skipcha Mountain Estates, is now available and looking for new homeowners! The open floor plan offers: 2-bedrooms downstairs, and 3, including the Master bedroom, on the second floor, 2-Living Areas plus a separate loft, eat-in kitchen with a formal dining room, large kitchen with an island and granite counter tops, Stainless steel appliances, and a separate laundry room. The backyard is ready for those Texas BBQ's! Come claim your home today! **OFFERING UP TO $10,000 INCENTIVE TOWARDS CLOSING COSTS-BRING ALL OFFERS!!**
